# Ledger directory (append-only)
#
# This directory contains immutable event logs:
# - observations.jsonl (raw facts)
# - decisions.jsonl (verdict records)
# - artifacts.jsonl (metadata about outputs)
#
# All files are append-only JSON lines (one JSON object per line).
# Never modify or delete past entries.
#
# Entries are added during daily runs:
# - OBS appends to observations.jsonl
# - TRI appends to decisions.jsonl
# - PUB appends decision metadata
# - MEM links entities in memory/index.json
#
# Git history shows cumulative growth of the ledger.
